name: Fast 201
description: The brand new F.A.S.T. 201 aka FAST201 with Fully Active Starburst Technology is designed for all levels of YoYo Players with style for doing sizzling hot tricks. This model features a unique Stainless Stell Ball bearing for super long spins. Comes with a a fully illustrated Quick Start Guide featuring a trick chart with 10 tricks. A spare string is also included with this deluxe package. Originally designed by YoHans Van Dan Elsen and Ben McPhee of the YoyoFactory, this new version offers the same great features and performance at a substantially lower price. Color and/or graphic design may vary from illustration.
